{"__type":"$$EventMessageAiNode","id":"f1b645c7-57a0-4256-8003-dab4278d6b5a","ts":"2025-09-30T09:38:35.291+02:00","eventName":"n8n.ai.llm.generated","message":"n8n.ai.llm.generated","payload":{"executionId":"137","nodeName":"Groq Chat Model1","workflowName":"My workflow 3","nodeType":"@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.lmChatGroq","workflowId":"QivgnSMUPDexbVcZ","msg":"{\"messages\":[\"System: You are a helpful assistant that extract informations from the incoming message and searches relevant sources online.\\n\\nStep 1: search online with \\\"Search with Tavily to extract urls\\\"\\nStep 2: filter the resulting urls, removing redundant hits and sorting them by degree of relevance\\nStep 3: Use Fetch to extract the markdown version of the website. \\n\\nStep 4: repeat the procedure (step 1-3) max 4 times. \\n\\nStep 5: return results and their sources. \\nWhich data was more common? \\nWhich one was not found to be founded?\\nHuman: ```json\\n[\\n  {\\n    \\\"projectName\\\": \\\"Luminora Solar Dos & Luminora Solar Tres (TotalEnergies + Soltec)\\\",\\n    \\\"locationName\\\": \\\"Murcia region\\\",\\n    \\\"organizationName\\\": \\\"TotalEnergies + Soltec\\\"\\n  },\\n  {\\n    \\\"projectName\\\": \\\"Luminora Solar Dos & Luminora Solar Tres (TotalEnergies + Soltec)\\\",\\n    \\\"locationName\\\": \\\"Murcia region\\\",\\n    \\\"organizationName\\\": \\\"TotalEnergies + Soltec\\\"\\n  },\\n  {\\n    \\\"projectName\\\": \\\"Entrenúcleos solar park (Plenitude – Eni)\\\",\\n    \\\"locationName\\\": \\\"Seville (Andalusia)\\\",\\n    \\\"organizationName\\\": \\\"Plenitude – Eni\\\"\\n  }\\n]\\n```\\nAI: I'll help you research these solar projects by following the steps you outlined.\\n\\n**Step 1: Search online with Tavily**\\nTool: [{\\\"query\\\":\\\"Luminora Solar Dos Luminora Solar Tres TotalEnergies Soltec Murcia region solar project\\\",\\\"follow_up_questions\\\":null,\\\"answer\\\":\\\"TotalEnergies and Soltec developed the Luminora Solar Dos and Tres projects in Murcia, Spain, with a combined capacity of 315 MW. Construction authorization was obtained, and the projects aim to supply electricity to over 30,000 homes. The projects are expected to reduce CO₂ emissions by 28,000 tons annually.\\\",\\\"images\\\":[],\\\"results\\\":[{\\\"url\\\":\\\"https://soltec.com/en/press-room/totalenergies-soltec-obtain-construction-authorization-200-mw-project-murcia/\\\",\\\"title\\\":\\\"Soltec obtain construction authorization for a 200 MW\\\",\\\"content\\\":\\\"TotalEnergies and Soltec obtain construction authorization for a 200 MW project in Murcia The Luminora Solar Dos photovoltaic project, with a capacity of 200 MW, developed by TotalEnergies, a multi-energy company, and Soltec, a vertically integrated photovoltaic company, in the Region of Murcia has received Administrative Construction Authorization. Image 3 2 July 2025 TotalEnergies and Soltec begin the construction of two new solar parks in the Region of Murcia View more Image 7 4 June 2025 Soltec completes the construction of a photovoltaic plant capable of supplying electricity to over 30,000 households and avoiding 28,000 tons of CO₂ emissions per year View more\\\",\\\"score\\\":0.8690161,\\\"raw_content\\\":null},{\\\"url\\\":\\\"https://www.nacleanenergy.com/solar/totalenergies-and-soltec-obtain-construction-authorization-for-a-200-mw-project-in-murcia\\\",\\\"title\\\":\\\"TotalEnergies and Soltec Obtain Construction ...\\\",\\\"content\\\":\\\"Published Time: Nov 06, 2023 North American Clean Energy - TotalEnergies and Soltec Obtain Construction Authorization for a 200 MW Project in Murcia *   Sponsored Content *   New Subscription;) *   Renew Subscription Allarticlesnews briefsproductssponsored content Nov 06, 2023 TotalEnergies and Soltec Obtain Construction Authorization for a 200 MW Project in Murcia The Luminora Solar Dos photovoltaic project, with a capacity of 200 MW, developed by **TotalEnergies**, a multi-energy company, and **Soltec**, a vertically integrated photovoltaic company, in the Region of Murcia has received Administrative Construction Authorization. Decarbonizing the economy is a major goal and we are particularly pleased to work on projects where biodiversity and communities are at the forefront. *   Sponsored Content By clicking ACCEPT or continuing to browse the site you are agreeing to our use of cookies.\\\",\\\"score\\\":0.8312667,\\\"raw_content\\\":null},{\\\"url\\\":\\\"https://renewablesnow.com/news/totalenergies-soltec-cut-sod-on-315-mw-of-solar-projects-in-spain-1277915/\\\",\\\"title\\\":\\\"TotalEnergies, Soltec cut sod on 315 MW of solar projects ...\\\",\\\"content\\\":\\\"Jul 3, 2025—The 220-MWLuminora Solar Dosand 95-MWLuminora Solar Tres projects, representing an investment of EUR 212 million (USD 250m), will cover 460\\\",\\\"score\\\":0.7482976,\\\"raw_content\\\":null},{\\\"url\\\":\\\"https://www.gem.wiki/Luminora_solar_farm\\\",\\\"title\\\":\\\"Luminora solar farm - Global Energy Monitor\\\",\\\"content\\\":\\\"Luminora solar farm - Global Energy Monitor Page **Luminora solar farm** (Planta solar fotovoltaica Luminora Solar) is a solar photovoltaic (PV) farm in pre-construction in Murcia, Region of Murcia, Spain. #### **Table 1:** Phase-level project details for Luminora solar farm #### **Table 2:** Phase-level location details for Luminora solar farm The map below shows the approximate locations of the solar farm phases: To access additional data, including an interactive map of global solar farms, a downloadable dataset, and summary data, please visit the Global Solar Power Tracker on the Global Energy Monitor website. id=BOE-A-2023-22641, https://murciaplaza.com/la-mega-planta-solar-de-total-y-soltec-en-murcia-san-pedro-y-san-javier-creara-2200-empleos https://www.pv-magazine.es/2023/01/20/mas-de-3-gws-fotovoltaicos-aprobados-en-enero-segun-el-boe/, https://www.boe.es/diario_boe/txt.php? id=BOE-A-2023-22641, https://murciaplaza.com/la-mega-planta-solar-de-total-y-soltec-en-murcia-san-pedro-y-san-javier-creara-2200-empleos.`{{cite web}}`: Check `|url=` value (help); Missing or empty `|title=` (help) 4.   ↑https://murciaplaza.com/la-mega-planta-solar-de-total-y-soltec-en-murcia-san-pedro-y-san-javier-creara-2200-empleos https://murciaplaza.com/la-mega-planta-solar-de-total-y-soltec-en-murcia-san-pedro-y-san-javier-creara-2200-empleos, https://murciaplaza.com/la-mega-planta-solar-de-total-y-soltec-en-murcia-san-pedro-y-san-javier-creara-2200-empleos.`{{cite web}}`: Check `|url=` value (help); Missing or empty `|title=` (help) title=Luminora_solar_farm&oldid=888661\\\\\\\"\\\",\\\"score\\\":0.72042775,\\\"raw_content\\\":null},{\\\"url\\\":\\\"https://newsroom.ferrovial.com/en-us/press-releases/ferrovial-to-build-three-photovoltaic-plants-in-murcia-spain-with-capacity-to-supply-30500-homes/\\\",\\\"title\\\":\\\"Ferrovial to build three photovoltaic plants in Murcia, Spain ...\\\",\\\"content\\\":\\\"TheLuminora Solar Tresplant, located in the municipalities ofMurciaand Torre Pacheco, will have a capacity of 95 MWp. Ferrovial will manage the design\\\",\\\"score\\\":0.65861565,\\\"raw_content\\\":null}],\\\"response_time\\\":1.69,\\\"request_id\\\":\\\"b7e817da-b8db-4ad3-9587-2b4a7201b08b\\\"}]\"],\"options\":{\"api_key\":{\"lc\":1,\"type\":\"secret\",\"id\":[\"GROQ_API_KEY\"]},\"model\":\"moonshotai/kimi-k2-instruct-0905\",\"temperature\":0.7},\"response\":{\"response\":{\"generations\":[[{\"text\":\"\",\"generationInfo\":{\"finish_reason\":\"tool_calls\"}}]]},\"tokenUsage\":{\"completionTokens\":38,\"promptTokens\":2179,\"totalTokens\":2217}}}"}}
