xpected to begin operations in 2026 and generate more than\\\",\\\"score\\\":0.87605256,\\\"raw_content\\\":null},{\\\"url\\\":\\\"https://energynews.pro/en/plenitude-starts-200-mw-solar-park-in-andalusia-for-2026/\\\",\\\"title\\\":\\\"Plenitude starts 200 MW solar park in Andalusia for 2026\\\",\\\"content\\\":\\\"Italian group Plenitude has begun building Entrenúcleos, a 200 MW photovoltaic plant near Seville, set to deliver more than 435 GWh a year from 2026.\\\",\\\"score\\\":0.8755427,\\\"raw_content\\\":null},{\\\"url\\\":\\\"https://energy-analytics-institute.org/2025/07/03/plenitude-starts-construction-of-new-200-mw-solar-park-in-spain-andalusia/\\\",\\\"title\\\":\\\"Plenitude starts construction of new 200 MW solar park in Spain ...\\\",\\\"content\\\":\\\"... Entrenúcleos, a new 200 MW photovoltaic project located in the municipalities of Dos Hermanas and Coria del Río, in the province of Seville (Andalusia).\\\",\\\"score\\\":0.87113565,\\\"raw_content\\\":null},{\\\"url\\\":\\\"https://www.akm.ru/eng/news/italian-subsidiary-eni-plenitude-expands-business-in-spain/\\\",\\\"title\\\":\\\"Italian subsidiary Eni Plenitude expands business in Spain - AK&M\\\",\\\"content\\\":\\\"The Entrenúcleos project, which will install 326,000 solar panels, is located in the municipalities of Dos Hermanas and Coria del Río in the province of Seville\\\",\\\"score\\\":0.8622012,\\\"raw_content\\\":null},{\\\"url\\\":\\\"https://www.power-technology.com/news/plenitude-200mw-pv-project-spain/\\\",\\\"title\\\":\\\"Plenitude begins construction of 200MW PV project in Spain\\\",\\\"content\\\":\\\"Entrenúcleos solar park is designed to consist of four plants: Granville, Killington, Plumlee and Rickwood.\\\",\\\"score\\\":0.79369855,\\\"raw_content\\\":null}],\\\"response_time\\\":0.98,\\\"request_id\\\":\\\"d4766a8f-16fb-45b3-97b9-00ca5e9f3b4d\\\"}]\"],\"options\":{\"api_key\":{\"lc\":1,\"type\":\"secret\",\"id\":[\"GROQ_API_KEY\"]},\"model\":\"moonshotai/kimi-k2-instruct-09